dc_description_s: This is a geodatabase of Planimetric Mapping Features: Montgomery County, Maryland, 2015. It was developed as part of the GeoMaP Pilot Project. The footprints are of a variety of structures including dwellings, businesses, houses, trailers, garages, etc. are present, and are attributed according to a feature coding scheme developed by the GeoMaP consortium.11/10/2015: Entire countywide building footprints updated by KUCERA INTERNATIONAL. Source date: 4/10/2014 imagery
dc_title_s: Planimetric Mapping Features: Montgomery County, Maryland, 2015
dc_publisher_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park and Planning Commission
